Diagnostic script in the repo

Added scripts\antigravity-diagnostic.ps1 so you can run the same process check the extension uses, without $_ being stripped when invoked from the shell.
Run it with:
powershell -NoProfile -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File "scripts\antigravity-diagnostic.ps1"
